CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Project Methodology object. This field set defines the methodology fields (if associated methodologies exist) to copy from a template to a new project. These fields are not displayed during creation of the project.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The API name of a field set used by the Methodology object. This field set defines the methodology fields (if associated methodologies exist) to copy from a template to a new project. These fields are not displayed during creation of the project.
CustomField.label: Project Methodology Hidden
